#

Pasta with Tomato Cream Sauce

30 min
$8
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

QuickEasyComfort FoodPasta

Description

A creamy, rich tomato sauce tossed with your favorite pasta for a comforting and delicious meal.

Ingredients

  • pasta: 8 oz
  • canned crushed tomatoes: 1 can (15 oz)
  • heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup
  • fresh basil (optional): for garnish
